ew/upload/sunn.jpg" alt="sunn / eater" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/10/sunn.php">sunn<br />eater</a></h4><p>音を重ねすぎず、シンプルなエレクトロサウンドとグルーヴがたまらなくなります。うるさすぎず高揚感のある楽曲が魅力です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000IB11RW?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000IB11RW" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'sunn-eater']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fsunn%252Fid388614503%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'sunn-eater']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/10/weather-report.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/weatherreport.jpg" alt="Weather Report / Caelum" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/10/weather-report.php">Weather Report<br />Caelum</a></h4><p>都会の雰囲気を感じさせるアーバンなサウンド。想像力をかき立てられるような音色やグルーヴが素晴らしい作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B001H9DEMY?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B001H9DEMY" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Weather Report-Caelum']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fweather-report%252Fid296620524%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Weather Report-Caelum']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/10/scale-of-rime.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/scaleofrime.jpg" alt="Scale of Rime / sooner" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/10/scale-of-rime.php">Scale of Rime<br />sooner</a></h4><p>目まぐるしく移り変わる音色に脳を刺激するようなクールなリズムアレンジ。盛り上がりたいときにかけたい1枚です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0021LSXPA?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0021LSXPA" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Scale of Rime-sooner']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fscale-of-rime%252Fid313164806%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Scale of Rime-sooner']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/10/7136.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/7136.jpg" alt="71:36 / Kiyo" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/10/7136.php">71:36<br />Kiyo</a></h4><p>神秘的な雰囲気を持つエレクトロ作品です。場の空気を変えたいときなどにもかけたくなるような作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B001E7OMDY?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B001E7OMDY" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', '71:36-Kiyo']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252F71-36%252Fid290698372%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', '71:36-Kiyo']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/10/president-idm.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/presidentidm.jpg" alt="President IDM / Geskia!" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/10/president-idm.php">President IDM<br />Geskia!</a></h4><p>盛り上がっきたときにはグルーヴが心地よいこの作品です。みんなで騒いだり踊ったりすることができる音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002D95LP0?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002D95LP0" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'President IDM-Geskia!']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fpresident-idm%252Fid360678334%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'President IDM-Geskia!']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/10/linear-cryptics.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/linearcryptics.jpg" alt="Linear Cryptics / Ametsub" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/10/linear-cryptics.php">Linear Cryptics<br />Ametsub</a></h4><p>クールなエレクトロニカ。繊細なアレンジが耳に刺激を送り込んでくれるような1枚です。何度も聴きたくなる作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00308B0GM?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00308B0GM" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Linear Cryptics-Ametsub']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Flinear-cryptics%252Fid388613943%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Linear Cryptics-Ametsub']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/10/mind-the-gap.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/mindthegap.jpg" alt="Mind The Gap / Nao Tokui" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/10/mind-the-gap.php">Mind The Gap<br />Nao Tokui</a></h4><p>躍動感のあるクールなリズムトラックが知性を感じさせる作品です。盛り上がりたいとき、またはまったりとしたいときのどちらにも合う音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003ULXTUY?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003ULXTUY" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Mind The Gap-Nao Tokui']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fmind-the-gap%252Fid388676303%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Mind The Gap-Nao Tokui']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div></div>

